==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Weakfish
<hw>Weak"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any fish of the genus <gen>Cynoscion</gen>; a squeteague; -- so
called from its tender mouth. See <er>Squeteague</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Spotted weakfish</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>the
spotted squeteague.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weak-hearted</ent>⟦br⟧
